snippet.textDisplay: You guys were commenting on the blood/liquid spreading from the shark's mouth in the Jaws 3-D clips. You thought maybe it was animation or something. snippet.authorDisplayName: Life of a Filmmaker on Balkans
snippet.textDisplay:
Imagine if Blade Runner was done in a garage 😲
Hi guys. My Youtube channel is engaged in Balkan filmmaking and I made an episode about an indy Sci-Fi short film from Croatia called Slice of Life.

https://youtu.be/uZYtNveSsEg

It took a lot of awards for short film around the world and it is in 5% of best Kickstarter campaigns for short film. Take a look and give me some feedback 😊

snippet.textDisplay: I watched a scene from the original Fright Night recently, the vampire was about to kill Charlie and got stabbed through the hand with a pencil. It showed him pull the pencil out THROUGH his hand in one shot with no cuts and no cg. I know it would be a super simple effect now but i was blown away by how well it was pulled off. It would be really cool to see you guys react to that
